Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.23,0:00:05.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將這片寂靜撕裂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.64,0:00:11.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引領整個世界\N來到熾熱之焰的最深處吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.95,0:00:33.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將我們的誓言\N灌注在朝天高舉的憤怒之拳中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.30,0:00:36.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再度點燃你的熱情吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.23,0:00:42.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,解放那沸騰不已的火紅熱血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.21,0:00:48.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論是誰都已無法阻止你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.54,0:00:55.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓一片黑暗的明天\N燃起希望的光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.42,0:01:00.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,化作捍衛弱者的獠牙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.96,0:01:03.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烈陽超重爆炎霸!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.23,0:01:15.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毫無畏懼的向前奔馳吧\N直到衝過那深紅色的終點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.37,0:01:23.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在最後一刻燃盡一切吧\N超重神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.71,0:01:53.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說回去後就要結婚了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.84,0:01:58.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊雖然等了很久\N但回到地上後馬上就會結婚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.51,0:02:02.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是漫長啊\N這一年的海底生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.02,0:02:05.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女朋友還猛向我吐苦水呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.15,0:02:09.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說她真不該愛上\N海底地熱發電中心的人員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.96,0:02:14.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就把累積一年的愛\N一次好好的愛她愛個夠就好了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.30,0:02:20.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「自浪濤的底層!」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.41,0:02:25.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到達目標海域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.34,0:02:27.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,視線良好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.34,0:02:31.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海面沒有發現異常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.42,0:02:38.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然得向我們求援\N看來EFA真的無計可施了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.96,0:02:42.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣異常發生了三天後\N才做的決策
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.89,0:02:44.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是讓人難以恭維
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.33,0:02:50.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G戰影轉換成潛艦模式\N開始潛航
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.92,0:03:09.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有異常非常的寧靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.26,0:03:15.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上要進入\NEFA海底地熱發電基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.86,0:03:18.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"海中基地"的營地區域內了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.87,0:03:25.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.97,0:03:28.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G...G戰影...反應消失...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.14,0:03:31.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露快回答\N莉露!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.18,0:03:35.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,切換到3.16頻道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.34,0:03:37.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有用完全無法接通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.91,0:03:42.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在地圖上無法確認誤差\N完全失去她的蹤影了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.62,0:03:48.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說朵莉雅\N莉露可能發生大麻煩了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.09,0:03:50.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再等一下下啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.76,0:03:53.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這陣子出擊使用的\N超重劍之力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.00,0:03:57.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓操作系統出現了\N一大堆錯誤嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.83,0:04:00.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我幫忙就是了\N快點弄好嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.67,0:04:05.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在是在做程式的調整\N英司少爺能幫的忙一件也...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.94,0:04:08.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你妨礙到維修了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.11,0:04:12.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朵莉雅\N現在立刻能出動的機體是那台?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.68,0:04:15.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G鑽機的維修已經完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.28,0:04:18.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有超重皇還是生龍活虎的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.22,0:04:23.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就讓這兩台潛入海底\N立刻做出動準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.39,0:04:25.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.13,0:04:27.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們得要看家啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.10,0:04:29.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也是無可奈何的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.63,0:04:32.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有時"等待"本身也是一種工作喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.27,0:04:34.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是他們幾個\N感覺上不太可靠嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.74,0:04:36.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還真不想被你這麼說喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.64,0:04:39.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會盡全力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.88,0:04:44.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我答應你英司\N我們一定會把G戰影帶回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.91,0:04:49.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比起G戰影\N救莉露這件事更優先喔你懂吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.45,0:04:54.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊...\N擔心莉露的人可不只你一個耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.10,0:05:09.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託只要一次就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.87,0:05:14.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?可是...\N我該怎麼辦呢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.48,0:05:18.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託啦\N我全都拜託妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.61,0:05:20.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司少爺...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.75,0:05:24.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那...只有一次...對嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.16,0:05:29.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太感謝妳了愛娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.29,0:05:34.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司少爺和愛娜\N他們是何時起變得這麼的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.33,0:05:36.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不行喔~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.10,0:05:42.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重要塞到達目標地點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.04,0:05:48.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重皇 G鑽機\N兩機請開始向海中潛航
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.58,0:05:49.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.15,0:06:01.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,螺旋槳模式啟動\N開始潛航
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.46,0:06:10.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛娜顯示海底狀況的螢幕\N就麻煩妳了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.37,0:06:12.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.60,0:06:16.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.87,0:06:19.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?\N愛娜人上哪去了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.24,0:06:23.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她...她說她突然肚子痛\N所以我才代替她...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.05,0:06:26.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要胡鬧了!\N你到底在想什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.88,0:06:30.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真...真的很對不起\N都怪我沒辦法拒絕...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.82,0:06:35.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳就不用在意了\N錯全都在這個傢伙頭上!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.52,0:06:38.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂! 你有沒有在聽啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.03,0:06:44.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我擔心斗牙...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.87,0:06:49.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那小子不是只要進入作戰狀態\N就會忽略周遭事物嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.87,0:06:53.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可別隨便亂轉鑽頭喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.05,0:07:01.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的為什麼那小子總是\N自作主張幹這種不用大腦的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.65,0:07:05.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別生氣了\N他的表現不也值得我們期待嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.16,0:07:08.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼嘛...原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.92,0:07:10.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是一點都不好玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.96,0:07:15.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這一帶吧\NG戰影就是在這附近消失的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.77,0:07:18.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是讓人有點擔心呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.73,0:07:22.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始分頭進行搜索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.21,0:07:32.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 G鑽機發動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.72,0:07:34.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.18,0:07:36.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓你亂轉鑽頭的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.85,0:07:39.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳別一直嘮叨這個好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.86,0:07:46.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.40,0:07:57.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到...到底發生了什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.84,0:08:01.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.12,0:08:15.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發現G戰影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.79,0:08:19.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機體外觀看起來沒有損傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.77,0:08:31.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星異種出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.76,0:08:51.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救莉露這件事第一優先喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.91,0:09:14.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳能活著真是太好了\N真的太好了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.12,0:09:18.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露...莉露...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.90,0:09:27.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳還好吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.73,0:09:28.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.63,0:09:31.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.84,0:09:34.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有哪裡會痛嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.64,0:09:37.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊...還好...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.61,0:09:38.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.74,0:09:43.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是EFA的海底基地\N"海中基地"的裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.18,0:09:48.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為外面有外星異種\N所以只好先躲進這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.05,0:09:53.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星異種在吸收海中基地?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.46,0:09:57.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然地熱發電工廠\N現在仍在運作中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.43,0:10:00.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是基地內部卻沒有動力可用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.00,0:10:04.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是被外星異種\N當做成長能源吸收掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.87,0:10:08.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,環境維持系統約有9成\N都處於停止狀態中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.74,0:10:12.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基地設施有6成以上\N正持續的和外星異種融合中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.68,0:10:18.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像是斗牙他們\N正身處外星異種體內呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.65,0:10:21.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是打算這樣在海底繼續成長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.45,0:10:24.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再向超重神挑戰吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.22,0:10:29.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主控室的系統還健全\N或許還有生存者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.73,0:10:31.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好開始進行搜索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.03,0:10:33.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.53,0:10:38.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到處都停電了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.30,0:10:41.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,氧氣供給也幾乎停止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.67,0:10:44.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這基地的人們都不要緊吧...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.07,0:10:46.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧莉露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.54,0:10:47.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.98,0:10:52.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然莉露也沒事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.72,0:10:55.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再來就只剩打倒外星異種了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.62,0:10:59.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙...開始改變了呢\N居然會為了別人挺身掩護
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.36,0:11:01.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不能這樣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.86,0:11:03.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有這麼說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.06,0:11:06.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊你...不准往這裡看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.46,0:11:07.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.43,0:11:10.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是故意要看的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.33,0:11:16.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明就是我\N和斗牙相處的時間比較久...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.44,0:11:20.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說\N靠我並沒辦法讓斗牙改變是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.04,0:11:51.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好慘啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.61,0:11:58.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來這裡已經沒有人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.82,0:12:04.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過這裡還真熱呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.19,0:12:08.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然聽說這裡是地熱發電基地...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.19,0:12:10.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是空調系統停止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.93,0:12:13.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺呼吸有點困難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.46,0:12:19.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是氧氣不足\N就像在高山上的感覺吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.07,0:12:21.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高山...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.84,0:12:24.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒爬過山\N所以不是很清楚...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.67,0:12:27.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也只有在書上讀過而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.28,0:12:27.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.11,0:12:29.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那本書上也有寫到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.88,0:12:33.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遇到山難的話\N會有狗狗帶白蘭地來喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.08,0:12:34.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.98,0:12:38.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我覺得帶可樂來的話\N我會更高興喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.82,0:12:41.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露妳有喝過可樂嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.36,0:12:43.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好喝的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.63,0:12:47.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次我們一起到城外去喝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.64,0:12:56.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星異種!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.52,0:13:09.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.52,0:13:11.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,往這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.82,0:13:19.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子...\N我們回不了停超重皇的船塢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.63,0:13:24.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣剩下的氧氣也會被耗光吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.83,0:13:29.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們到主控室去吧\N那邊的系統應該還能運作才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.62,0:13:44.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.82,0:13:47.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露妳帶著這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.56,0:13:51.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子就動不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.49,0:13:53.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然的確會讓機動性降低\N但是威力很大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.00,0:13:56.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能在被靠近前就打倒對方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.93,0:14:00.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算我死了\N有這個妳就不要緊了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.04,0:14:03.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要這麼說呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.44,0:14:06.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.58,0:14:10.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隔離壁被突破了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.98,0:14:14.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡我來擋著\N妳快到主控室去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.42,0:14:15.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.29,0:14:17.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.69,0:14:19.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.82,0:14:21.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留下你一個人的話\N那我更不能走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.76,0:14:24.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要有這把槍\N不就能打倒那些敵人了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.03,0:14:28.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在英司他們趕到之前\N我不想多做任何浪費
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.56,0:14:30.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,包括剩下的氧氣量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.60,0:14:34.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可以...我不要\N你也得和我一起才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.50,0:14:37.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是一起的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.68,0:14:48.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.92,0:14:51.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.69,0:14:55.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙...斗牙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.19,0:14:59.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露怎麼了?\N妳在哭嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.19,0:15:00.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙他怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.23,0:15:04.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓我逃走\N他一個人和外星異種...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.67,0:15:08.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上趕去\N妳就留在那裡別動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.17,0:15:15.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要再失去任何人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.30,0:15:36.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隔離壁的解除碼是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.34,0:15:43.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星異種!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.77,0:15:46.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吸收了基地的能源\N然後變成這副德性是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.94,0:15:51.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在完成同化之前\N我們就挖過牠正下方的岩盤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.35,0:15:53.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直接衝到斗牙身邊去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.62,0:16:01.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的對手在這裡喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.89,0:16:06.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點! 英司、琉菜\N外面的傢伙我們來纏住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.43,0:16:08.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媚月大姊可真有妳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.56,0:16:10.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要謝的話去謝朵莉雅吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.53,0:16:13.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她可是拼了命\N用全速把我們這兩架維修完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.34,0:16:15.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那駕駛G攻擊機的是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.87,0:16:18.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我...對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.88,0:16:29.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.73,0:16:42.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有我一個人能得救的話\N那我一點也不高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.07,0:16:46.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.70,0:16:49.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.35,0:16:58.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙! 莉露!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.25,0:17:00.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司琉菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.08,0:17:03.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個都沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.22,0:17:06.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你...你們...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.52,0:17:08.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底在做什麼啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.36,0:17:14.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重皇超重機組\N全機集合完畢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.40,0:17:16.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.27,0:17:27.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重戰騎的諸位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.88,0:17:30.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啟動合神!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.68,0:17:31.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.82,0:17:37.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重...合神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.08,0:18:03.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重弧光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.55,0:18:15.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂斗牙\N你在搞什麼啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.19,0:18:20.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?斗牙失去視力了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.20,0:18:23.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,推測是長期處於缺氧狀態\N而造成的情形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.58,0:18:38.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙振作點啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.88,0:18:40.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂! 怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.08,0:18:42.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.25,0:18:43.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.79,0:18:45.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我過去他那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.02,0:18:49.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?等一下\N莉露妳要做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.80,0:19:06.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胸部駕駛艙移轉為幽靈系統了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.01,0:19:10.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰力降低...打擊真不小呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.01,0:19:13.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.63,0:19:29.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.70,0:19:31.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.47,0:19:33.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成為你的眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.94,0:19:37.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.21,0:19:45.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重劍招來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.39,0:20:01.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工學暴風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.87,0:20:10.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在! 斗牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.71,0:20:14.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超.重.斬!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.41,0:20:48.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爺\N要不要再繼續躺一下比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.44,0:20:49.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不要緊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.11,0:20:52.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳愛娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.35,0:20:56.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起\N讓你發生了這麼嚴重的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.45,0:21:01.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別在意啦\N保護女孩子本來就是男人的責任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.86,0:21:04.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家也好想要被人守護喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.33,0:21:07.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳哪還需要別人保護啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.20,0:21:09.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你多什麼嘴啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.37,0:21:16.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"報復"可是女人的當然權利喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.17,0:21:19.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可得記好囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.27,0:21:23.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司你真的好喜歡摔跤呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.48,0:21:25.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少管我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.78,0:21:29.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過看來你也開始\N有點自覺了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.72,0:21:31.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼自覺?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.32,0:21:32.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男子漢的自覺啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.92,0:21:35.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"即使是逞強也要保護妳"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.36,0:21:39.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那樣子的心情懂了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.43,0:21:41.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.30,0:21:44.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都能平安無事\N真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.74,0:22:04.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因熱戀而無法成眠的夜晚\N已經看膩了星座占卜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.22,0:22:12.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為想要聽到人的聲音\N所以隨意打了電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.69,0:22:21.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了靠不住的語音留言\N你現在到底在哪裡呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.20,0:22:28.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,映著冰箱內的燈光\N我在狹小的宇宙裡彷徨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.04,0:22:37.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你給我的唱片\N唱針已經跳開不知幾次了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.55,0:22:44.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我相信這不變的溫度\N一直到什麼時候?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.96,0:22:46.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OHBABY
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.56,0:22:53.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我耳邊輕語嘛\N對讓我聽聽你溫柔的聲音嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.44,0:22:56.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們手牽手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.47,0:23:03.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一同被沁入你心中的\N淺淺呼吸籠罩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.58,0:23:10.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我耳邊輕語嘛\N對讓我聽聽你溫柔的聲音嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.52,0:23:13.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們閉上眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.46,0:23:21.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一同在溜進你夢中的\N甜美節奏中融化吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.30,0:23:31.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是警備女僕庫琪\N下回的舞台是...遊樂園!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.47,0:23:32.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是大家一起去那裡玩嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.97,0:23:34.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的是很嚴肅的調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.84,0:23:38.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在一一發生的怪異事件\N與看不見身影的外星異種前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.75,0:23:41.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神陷入了前所未有的危機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.38,0:23:44.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼大的敵人\N要怎麼樣才能打贏呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.92,0:23:47.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,此外\N還有令人意外的事實將會揭開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.19,0:23:49.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下回「夢想的孤島」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.32,0:23:52.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下回我們也將照料各位的和平


